  description: "V\u0129nh Long l\xE0 m\u1ED9t t\u1EC9nh thu\u1ED9c v\xF9ng \u0110\u1ED3ng
    b\u1EB1ng s\xF4ng C\u1EEDu Long \u1EDF ph\xEDa Nam c\u1EE7a Vi\u1EC7t Nam. T\u1EC9nh
    n\u1EB1m gi\u1EEFa hai con s\xF4ng l\u1EDBn l\xE0 s\xF4ng Ti\u1EC1n v\xE0 s\xF4ng
    H\u1EADu, t\u1EA1o n\xEAn h\u1EC7 th\u1ED1ng s\xF4ng ng\xF2i v\xE0 k\xEAnh r\u1EA1ch
    d\xE0y \u0111\u1EB7c. Trung t\xE2m c\u1EE7a t\u1EC9nh l\xE0 th\xE0nh ph\u1ED1
    V\u0129nh Long. M\u1ED9t s\u1ED1 \u0111\u1ECBa danh n\u1ED5i b\u1EADt c\u1EE7a
    t\u1EC9nh g\u1ED3m C\xF9 lao An B\xECnh v\xE0 V\u0103n Th\xE1nh Mi\u1EBFu V\u0129nh
    Long.\n\nV\u0129nh Long n\u1ED5i ti\u1EBFng v\u1EDBi nhi\u1EC1u \u0111\u1EB7c
    s\u1EA3n tr\xE1i c\xE2y v\xE0 m\xF3n \u0103n mi\u1EC1n s\xF4ng n\u01B0\u1EDBc
    nh\u01B0 Cam s\xE0nh Tam B\xECnh, Khoai lang B\xECnh T\xE2n v\xE0 C\xE1 tai t\u01B0\u1EE3ng
    chi\xEAn x\xF9.\n\nV\u1EC1 v\u0103n h\xF3a, V\u0129nh Long mang \u0111\u1EADm
    n\xE9t v\u0103n h\xF3a s\xF4ng n\u01B0\u1EDBc c\u1EE7a v\xF9ng T\xE2y Nam B\u1ED9
    v\u1EDBi c\xE1c ho\u1EA1t \u0111\u1ED9ng sinh ho\u1EA1t tr\xEAn s\xF4ng, v\u01B0\u1EDDn
    c\xE2y tr\xE1i v\xE0 c\xE1c l\xE0n \u0111i\u1EC7u d\xE2n ca \u0111\u1EB7c tr\u01B0ng
    nh\u01B0 \u0110\u1EDDn ca t\xE0i t\u1EED Nam B\u1ED9, lo\u1EA1i h\xECnh ngh\u1EC7
    thu\u1EADt \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c UNESCO c\xF4ng nh\u1EADn l\xE0 Di s\u1EA3n
    v\u0103n h\xF3a phi v\u1EADt th\u1EC3 c\u1EE7a nh\xE2n lo\u1EA1i."
  desSatNhap: "T\u1EEB ng\xE0y 1/7/2025, ba t\u1EC9nh B\u1EBFn Tre, Tr\xE0 Vinh v\xE0
    V\u0129nh Long ch\xEDnh th\u1EE9c s\xE1p nh\u1EADp th\xE0nh m\u1ED9t \u0111\u01A1n
    v\u1ECB h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh m\u1EDBi mang t\xEAn t\u1EC9nh V\u0129nh ong. T\u1EC9nh
    m\u1EDBi c\xF3 di\u1EC7n t\xEDch kho\u1EA3ng 6.296,2km vu\xF4ng \r          ,
    quy m\xF4 d\xE2n s\u1ED1 g\u1EA7n 4,2 tri\u1EC7u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi, v\u1EDBi trung
    t\xE2m h\xE0nh ch\xEDnh \u0111\u1EB7t t\u1EA1i TP. V\u0129nh Long hi\u1EC7n nay.
    Vi\u1EC7c h\u1EE3p nh\u1EA5t nh\u1EB1m t\u1EA1o kh\xF4ng gian ph\xE1t tri\u1EC3n
    m\u1EDBi v\xE0 tinh g\u1ECDn b\u1ED9 m\xE1y."
